scene.message:
Yukino: Even though they're{nl}
our own, seeing them like{nl}
this is strange, huh.{waitkey}Personas, that is.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: They said "world of{nl}
the dead," so I figured it'd{nl}
be scarier, but it's not{waitkey}so bad.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A place where the{nl}
souls of the dead gather.{nl}
Not pleasant, but in a{waitkey}sense a solemn place too.{waitkey}{clearbox}It makes me feel, somehow,{nl}
as though I should{nl}
straighten up.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: When I die, I'm 100{nl}
percent going to heaven!{waitkey}{clearbox}So this is my last look at{nl}
the scenery of the{nl}
"afterlife"! Yep, yep.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: This is a little{nl}
different from the Hell{nl}
Image we imagine,{waitkey}this place.{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: What is this place?{nl}
Now and then, things like{nl}
your astral bodies appear{waitkey}on the walls around us!{waitkey}{clearbox}I got great photos, so I'll{nl}
give you some once they're{nl}
developed! A photo of your{waitkey}own ghost is a rare thing!{waitkey}{ret}

???: Oh, hello!{nl}
Nice to meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm Mariko Yabe of the{nl}
"Yamagumo Private High School{nl}
Paranormal Club"! Nice to{waitkey}meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Though it's an unofficial club{nl}
where I'm both president and{nl}
sole member!{waitkey}{clearbox}My homeroom teacher won't{nl}
approve the club just because{nl}
he says it's "lame"!{waitkey}{clearbox}So today I came to meet my{nl}
comrade Kuroori, but...{nl}
never{wait_fr:30} did I think...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'd get caught up in such an{nl}
amazing paranormal event!{nl}
I'm, like, super lucky!{waitkey}{clearbox}I've been snapping photos like{nl}
crazy! And I'll submit these{nl}
demon photos to a magazine!{waitkey}{clearbox}Then! Maybe the teacher will{nl}
approve the club after all!{nl}
Alright! I'll do my best!{waitkey}{ret}
